_sText:
Everything in the map glows apart from the black, simple layout with rewards for reaching the other side :) the light on the floor at the back of your opponents base teleports you to an awp spot and gives u autoawp :D

HDR must be enabled for glowing effect

36 Spawns
Custom .vmt's by cH3wY
Custom .vtf's by mekaonija

Just copy and paste into maps folder, custom textures are included in the .bsp
